This is a Beaconpush library for Android based on the Beaconpish REST API: http://beaconpush.com/guide/rest-api/

This Android project is a library project (http://developer.android.com/tools/projects/index.html#LibraryProjects) that can be integrated with your Android application.
name: Beaconpush library for Android
